dct_description_sm: Map of the Ligurian coast, also known as the Italian Riviera, west of Genoa. Relief shown pictorially. German text on verso with running title: Der Staat Genua am Westen; p. 23; signature P. From: Novus Atlas, das ist, Weltbeschreibung ... / durch Guil. Joh. Blaeu. Amsterdam : Joh. Guil F. Blaeu, 1647-55. Vol. 3.
